column1: Kore ga mondai desu ne? Ima Purincessu Kenni sugoi irimasu!
Hayai de! Purincessu Kennu, arigato! Mondai dayo: XBokusu saisho no Bill Gates watashi no PS4 shipment tomatteimasu!
Taihen. Kono console warusu mada owaranai.
Purincessu Kenni, honto ni zenbu arigato
You will not interfere, Bill Gates! These-a children will get their PS4s!
Then let this be your last fight, Bill Gates.
